            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>加重结直肠癌的病菌竟来自口腔？】越来越多的癌症，被发现与细菌或病毒的感染相关。作为死亡率第二高的癌症，结直肠癌全球每年的发病人数高达190万，而死亡人数高达93万。那么，会不会有某种细菌或病毒跟结直肠癌的发病或恶化有关呢？科学家是如何在口腔中找到元凶的？👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%96%B0%E9%B2%9C%E4%BA%8B%E5%84%BF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%96%B0%E9%B2%9C%E4%BA%8B%E5%84%BF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫新鲜事儿#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> （出品：科普中国） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4925949754671170" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">科普中国的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/005ztyuLly1hg4imtzg0mj61hc0u0nj102.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/UR2BTDtNlx087bfVo6Yw01041202rah60E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690089265&amp;ssig=uWJteWUZ0a&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/KHbkTFERlx087bfUYkMw01041201c9Wb0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690089265&amp;ssig=AbeucW3CgI&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/6UndTGEnlx087bfV1tMs01041200J75P0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690089265&amp;ssig=du