            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>提醒！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%8D%E5%A4%8D%E5%8F%91%E7%83%A7%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E5%B7%9D%E5%B4%8E%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%8D%E5%A4%8D%E5%8F%91%E7%83%A7%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E5%B7%9D%E5%B4%8E%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#孩子反复发烧警惕川崎病#</span></a>】川崎病是一种儿童常见病，春夏季是高发期。前期症状与感冒非常相似，表现为反复发热，过程中可能出现皮疹、双眼结膜充血、颈部淋巴结肿大、手指脚趾末端肿起等。专家介绍，川崎病的主要危害是获得性心脏病，损伤严重会出现冠脉动脉瘤等并发症。不过，若早发现、早治疗，愈后也可良好。 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4925875230277665" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hg4a2yphv5j61hw0ub4qp02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/nN92H5f6lx087aVdMZ3a01041200DlMy0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690089262&amp;ssig=BzbaW96jys&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/9wnTbSEtlx087aVb5ZNK01041200kq4D0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690089262&amp;ssig=J%2FUqepzXDL&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/z2YD5jXDlx087aVaOCco01041200d36h0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690089262&amp;ssig=QLeLEkyfYm&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4925875230277665&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
